language Essence 1.4

letting R1 be domain record { a : bool, b : int(0..9) }

letting M1 be domain matrix indexed by [int(2, 4, 6)] of int(1..4)
letting R2 be domain record { b: int(3, 5..7), c: M1 }

letting T1 be domain tuple(int(1..3), bool)

letting R be domain record { x: R1, y: R2, z: T1 }

find r: R
such that
  r[x] = record { b = 5, a = true },
  r[x][b] > r[y][b],
  allDiff(r[y][c]),
  sum(r[y][c]) <= r[y][b] * 2,
  r[z] = (2, false)
